\af[2]\N<\n[2]>A goblin! It's still alive, let's finish it off.
\af[6]\N<\n[6]>This thing was probably with the party that raided Edge.
\N<Goblin>Please humans, I'm injured, I wasn't with the party that raided your shacks. Just me and my buddy\..\..\.. we were looking for food.
\N<Goblin>A bear surprised us at night. And it killed Goldrak!
The goblin wimpers, glancing over at its dead friend.
